
@{

    Layout = null; // Disables the layout for this view
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_LayoutCustomer.cshtml";
}
<section class="customer_service_section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="detail-box">
                    <div class="heading_container">
                        <h2>Customer Service</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>At Eflyer, our top priority is to provide an exceptional shopping experience for our customers. We understand the importance of reliable and efficient customer service, and our team is dedicated to assisting you with any inquiries or concerns you may have.</p>

                    <h3>How Can We Help You?</h3>

                    <h4>Product Inquiries:</h4>
                    <p>Have questions about a product? Our knowledgeable team is here to provide you with detailed information to help you make informed purchasing decisions. Whether you need specifics about materials, sizing, or functionality, we’re here to help.</p>

                    <h4>Order Assistance:</h4>
                    <p>If you need help with placing an order, tracking a shipment, or understanding your order status, our customer service representatives are ready to assist you. We strive to make the ordering process smooth and hassle-free.</p>

                    <h4>Returns and Exchanges:</h4>
                    <p>We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If for any reason you are not, our return and exchange policy is designed to be straightforward and easy. Contact our customer service team to initiate a return or exchange, and we will guide you through the process.</p>

                    <h4>Technical Support:</h4>
                    <p>Encountering technical issues with our website? Our support team can help troubleshoot and resolve any problems you may be experiencing, ensuring you have a seamless shopping experience.</p>

                    <h4>Feedback and Suggestions:</h4>
                    <p>Your feedback is invaluable to us. We welcome your suggestions on how we can improve our products and services. If you have any ideas or feedback, please do not hesitate to reach out.</p>

                    <h3>Contact Us</h3>

                    <h4>Email:</h4>
                    <p>For any inquiries or support, please email us at <a href="mailto:customer.service@youronlinestore.com">customer.service@youronlinestore.com</a>. Our team will respond within 24 hours to address your needs.</p>

                    <h4>Phone:</h4>
                    <p>Speak directly with a customer service representative by calling Eflyer. Our phone lines are open Monday to Friday from 9 AM to 6 PM.</p>

                    <h4>Live Chat:</h4>
                    <p>For immediate assistance, use our live chat feature available on our website. Our representatives are online and ready to help during business hours.</p>

                    <h4>Social Media:</h4>
                    <p>Connect with us on Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter for the latest updates, promotions, and to send us direct messages with any inquiries.</p>

                    <p>Thank you for choosing Eflyer. We are committed to providing you with outstanding customer service and ensuring your shopping experience is enjoyable and stress-free.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

